<br>
Also please look at my stuff and tell me where I could upgrade, I'd rather save my cash for a nice 2HB (Peacebringer).  Only have about 800pp in bank.  I also have a 51 druid but don't want to stop the exp grind to farm trash to sell with him.<br>
<br>
