<br>
All prices on Prexus.<br>
<br>
1. Face: Acrylia Reinforced Mask.  A steal at 100pp and a good purchase at 200pp for 7AC and stats, but a Cougarskin mask quest item is available at 6ac, a silvery mask (5AC, 25hp) for 50pp.<br>
<br>
2.  Collar:  Spider Fur for 200pp.  Ulthork for under 100pp.<br>
<br>
3.  Head: Replace Exec hood with Turban in your bag.<br>
<br>
4.  Wrists: 7AC Vox bracers 2 for total of 60pp. (mine were 55).  Very cheap upgrade!<br>
<br>
5.  Hands:  Gem Inlaid Gauntlets (8AC plus Dex) for 50pp or so. Nice upgrade.  Or get them yourself.<br>
<br>
6.  Sleeves:  Azure Sleeves for 150-200pp.  Bought mine for 150pp.  Hard to beat the 12AC at that price.<br>
<br>
7.  Shoulders:  Greyhopper.  A Tailor will do it for skill up usually. 8AC/ 0.4 wt.<br>
<br>
If you have 250pp left, and I would probably do without spider fur collar, then go for a Goranga Idol in Range slot (8AC and nice stats incl HP).  After a few hundred plat more, you might want to sell FBSS and replace with SCHW/Spider Fur belt.<br>
<br>
Now, as for a nice 2HB, you got one already!  Baton of Faith is very nice.  I saw a staff of battle (31/37) for 1000pp last night, but was out of funds.  /cry.<br>
<br>
If you head for CC and the geonids, the plat will come in.  Be warned though that the geos are often camped for hours on end by high-level monks farming cash for upgrades.  What a novel idea!<br>
<br>
Lorianne Moonraker<br>
